{
  "stem": "4187.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were-- well, first of all, we all had to hang around for a long time before something happened.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, eventually we were taken out of Lager C, and we were taken somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were told that we're going to be put on the train straightaway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, we weren't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And apparently something happened to the-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Train wasn't available, whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they said that for all the night, we're going to go over to another lager.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that-- again, I've got to say that my memory is slightly different from my sister's, but I'm going to stick to mine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were taken into another compound, and we were set down on the ground there, waiting.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And women were coming down looking for relatives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And whenever someone came in, people were always looked, naturally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And these women came down looking for relatives, and some- someone asked names.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who are you all?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we all said our names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, they were all-- there was always, have you met such and such?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She looks such and such.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you remember her?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was constant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Has anyone seen anyone?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we gave our name, and that-- that's it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The person went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then not too long after that we saw a figure running down this camp street calling our name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Someone had heard our name, being Scheffer, and my mother was the camp doctor, so her name was known, and went up to her and said, I think your daughters are there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are two girls there called Scheffer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what can I say?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, we didn't know whether she was alive or dead, although my sister says that we knew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember that I knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
